</p>

<p class="jp">
大覚寺に隣接する大沢池の菊ヶ島には、鳥たちが集まってくる。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Kyoto" /><category term="Ponds" /><category term="Black and White" /><category term="Temples" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Birds hang out on Kikugashima island in Osawa Ike pond, adjacent to Daikaku-ji temple.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2501_IMG_0903_jpg.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2501_IMG_0903_jpg.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Funehashi-ya・船はしや</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250130/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Funehashi-ya・船はしや" /><published>2025-01-30T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2025-01-30T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/funehashiya</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250130/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
